---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Studio — Digital PR Agency for Higher Education" description="701am Studio — digital PR agency for higher education. Earned media campaigns, data-story pitches, journalist outreach, and AI visibility. $6,500 per engagement, up to 50 placements.">
<!-- HERO -->
<header class="ind-hero" id="top">
  <div class="hero-atmos"><div class="grid"></div><div class="glow g1"></div><div class="glow g2"></div><div class="glow g3"></div></div>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="ind-eyebrow"><a class="bk" href="/">701am</a> / Studio</div>
    <h1>The digital PR agency <em class="grad">higher education trusts</em>.</h1>
    <p class="isub">Earned media campaigns that get your institution in Inside Higher Ed, regional press, and the publications your applicants already read. <b>Up to 50 placements per engagement. No long-term retainer.</b></p>
    <div class="hero-ctas">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-studio"><i class="ti ti-calendar"></i>Book a discovery call</a>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-soft btn-lg"><i class="ti ti-sparkles"></i>$500 intro session</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- TRUST STRIP -->
<section class="band wrap" style="padding-top:0;padding-bottom:14px">
  <div class="studio-note" style="max-width:100%;text-align:center;justify-content:center">
    <i class="ti ti-shield-check"></i>
    <div>
      <strong>Earned media only.</strong> We don't place sponsored content without labeling it. Every placement we earn is real coverage — written by journalists, shaped by real news value, and credible to prospective students.
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SERVICES -->
<section class="band wrap" id="services">
  <div class="sec-head">
    <div class="sec-eyebrow">Our services</div>
    <h2>Everything earned media needs. <em class="grad">Scopped and delivered.</em></h2>
    <p>From data-story research through journalist outreach and AI citation tracking — every campaign is managed start to finish.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="studio-cards">
    <div class="scard">
      <span class="sc-tag" style="background:var(--coral-soft);color:var(--coral-deep)">Earned Media</span>
      <h3>Earned Media Campaigns</h3>
      <p>Full-cycle earned media campaigns — from data-story research and narrative development through journalist outreach, placement tracking, and funnel correlation. Every placement earns coverage that compounds into search authority and AI citations.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Data-story research & narrative development</li>
        <li>Journalist research & reporter relationship management</li>
        <li>Pitch writing & outreach (human-written, not AI-spammed)</li>
        <li>Placement tracking & coverage reporting</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="sc-foot">
        <div class="sc-best">Best for <b>universities, enrollment teams</b></div>
        <div class="sc-price">$6,500 / engagement · up to 50 placements</div>
        <a href="/contact" class="sc-cta">Book a discovery call <i class="ti ti-calendar"></i></a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="scard">
      <span class="sc-tag" style="background:var(--amber-soft);color:var(--amber-deep)">Data Stories</span>
      <h3>Data-Story Campaigns</h3>
      <p>Your institution has data that reporters want — enrollment patterns, salary outcomes, completion rates, regional comparisons. We find the angle, write the pitch, and work the list so your data earns the coverage it deserves.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Data audit & angle identification</li>
        <li>Story framing & methodology documentation</li>
        <li>Pitch writing & journalist outreach</li>
        <li>Coverage amplification & follow-up</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="sc-foot">
        <div class="sc-best">Best for <b>programs with strong outcomes data</b></div>
        <div class="sc-price">$6,500 / engagement · up to 50 placements</div>
        <a href="/contact" class="sc-cta">Book a discovery call <i class="ti ti-calendar"></i></a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="scard">
      <span class="sc-tag" style="background:var(--indigo-soft);color:var(--indigo-deep)">AI Visibility</span>
      <h3>AI Citation Strategy</h3>
      <p>When prospective students ask ChatGPT which program is best, your institution needs to be in the answer. We earn the signals — rankings, outcomes data, press coverage — that AI models learn from and cite.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>AI citation audit & competitive analysis</li>
        <li>Signals strategy — what to earn and where</li>
        <li>Integration with earned media campaigns</li>
        <li>Quarterly AI visibility reporting</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="sc-foot">
        <div class="sc-best">Best for <b>programs competing for AI-shortlisted applicants</b></div>
        <div class="sc-price">$6,500 / engagement · up to 50 placements</div>
        <a href="/contact" class="sc-cta">Book a discovery call <i class="ti ti-calendar"></i></a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="scard">
      <span class="sc-tag" style="background:var(--slate-soft);color:var(--slate-blue)">Thought Leadership</span>
      <h3>Executive Positioning</h3>
      <p>Position your leadership in the publications, podcasts, and platforms that your audience trusts. Bylines, speaking slots, and panel placements — built around genuine expertise, not manufactured narratives.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Topic identification & story angle development</li>
        <li>Bylines & contributed articles</li>
        <li>Podcast & speaking placement</li>
        <li>Quote sourcing for journalists</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="sc-foot">
        <div class="sc-best">Best for <b>university leadership, edtech executives</b></div>
        <div class="sc-price">$6,500 / engagement · up to 50 placements</div>
        <a href="/contact" class="sc-cta">Book a discovery call <i class="ti ti-calendar"></i></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PRICING -->
<section class="band wrap" id="pricing">
  <div class="sec-head">
    <div class="sec-eyebrow">Pricing</div>
    <h2>Simple pricing. <em class="grad">No retainers.</em></h2>
    <p>Every engagement is scoped to deliver a specific number of placements. Start with a $500 session to find your story — or book a discovery call to scope your campaign.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="pricing-cmp" style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto">
    <div class="pcard">
      <div class="pc-head">
        <div class="pc-icon" style="background:var(--amber-soft);color:var(--amber-deep)"><i class="ti ti-sparkles"></i></div>
        <div>
          <div class="pc-label">Earned Media Session</div>
          <div class="pc-sub">90-minute strategy session</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pc-price">
        <span class="pc-amt">$500</span>
        <span class="pc-per">one-time</span>
      </div>
      <ul class="pc-feat">
        <li><i class="ti ti-check"></i>90-minute strategy session with our team</li>
        <li><i class="ti ti-check"></i>Data audit — find the stories you're not telling</li>
        <li><i class="ti ti-check"></i>Reporter list for your top 3 angles</li>
        <li><i class="ti ti-check"></i>Credibility gap analysis</li>
        <li><i class="ti ti-check"></i>No obligation to continue</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-soft btn-lg" style="width:100%;margin-top:8px"><i class="ti ti-calendar"></i>Book your session</a>
    </div>
    <div class="pcard pcard-701">
      <div class="pc-launch"><span class="pc-dot"></span>Most common engagement</div>
      <div class="pc-head">
        <div class="pc-icon pc-icon-grad"><i class="ti ti-rocket"></i></div>
        <div>
          <div class="pc-label" style="color:#fff">Earned Media Engagement</div>
          <div class="pc-sub" style="color:var(--night-txt)">Full campaign · up to 50 placements</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pc-price">
        <span class="pc-amt pc-amt-grad">$6,500</span>
        <span class="pc-per" style="color:var(--night-txt)">per engagement</span>
      </div>
      <ul class="pc-feat pc-feat-dark">
        <li><i class="ti ti-check"></i>Full campaign — research, narrative, pitches</li>
        <li><i class="ti ti-check"></i>Up to 50 placements in target outlets</li>
        <li><i class="ti ti-check"></i>AI citation tracking & optimization</li>
        <li><i class="ti ti-check"></i>Monthly reporting & strategy review</li>
        <li><i class="ti ti-check"></i>No long-term contract</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" style="width:100%;margin-top:8px"><i class="ti ti-calendar"></i>Book a discovery call</a>
      <div class="pc-fine">Most engagements complete in 8–12 weeks.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
<section class="layer-sec">
  <div class="atmos"><div class="dg dg1"></div></div>
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="wrap inner">
      <div class="sec-head">
        <div class="eb" style="color:#E89B7E">Our process</div>
        <h2 style="color:#fff">From story to <em class="grad">placement</em>.</h2>
        <p style="color:var(--night-txt)">Every engagement follows a proven four-step methodology.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="layers">
        <div class="layer"><div class="num">01</div><h3><i class="ti ti-search"></i>Discover</h3><p>We audit your current coverage, data assets, and competitive position. We find the stories you're not telling and the outlets most likely to cover them.</p></div>
        <div class="layer"><div class="num">02</div><h3><i class="ti ti-pencil"></i>Develop</h3><p>We find the angle, frame the data, and write the pitch. Every story is built around genuine news value — not invented narratives.</p></div>
        <div class="layer"><div class="num">03</div><h3><i class="ti ti-send"></i>Deploy</h3><p>We work the reporter list — human outreach, not mass emails. We place with journalists who actually cover your space, and follow up to maximize placement odds.</p></div>
        <div class="layer"><div class="num">04</div><h3><i class="ti ti-report-analytics"></i>Report</h3><p>We track every placement, correlate it to search and AI visibility, and report on what moved — not vanity metrics.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHY STUDIO -->
<section class="band wrap">
  <div class="sec-head">
    <div class="sec-eyebrow">Why 701am Studio</div>
    <h2>Not a traditional agency. <em class="grad">Built for this.</em></h2>
    <p>We've spent two decades in education visibility — not as spectators, but as the people who built the properties millions of prospective students used to compare programs.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="diffs">
    <div class="diff">
      <div class="diff-icon" style="background:var(--coral-soft);color:var(--coral-deep)"><i class="ti ti-school"></i></div>
      <div>
        <h3>Higher ed is all we do</h3>
        <p>We don't serve every industry. Depth beats breadth — and we've spent 20 years on this exact corner of the media landscape.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="diff">
      <div class="diff-icon" style="background:var(--amber-soft);color:var(--amber-deep)"><i class="ti ti-chart-bar"></i></div>
      <div>
        <h3>Data first</h3>
        <p>Every campaign starts with data — outcomes, enrollment patterns, regional comparisons. The best stories are already in your institutional data; we just find them and pitch them.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="diff">
      <div class="diff-icon" style="background:var(--indigo-soft);color:var(--indigo-deep)"><i class="ti ti-robot"></i></div>
      <div>
        <h3>AI visibility built in</h3>
        <p>Every placement earns signals that AI models cite. We optimize for human journalists AND the AI assistants that now shape your applicant pipeline.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="diff">
      <div class="diff-icon" style="background:var(--green-soft);color:var(--green-deep)"><i class="ti ti-arrows-up-right"></i></div>
      <div>
        <h3>Compounding coverage</h3>
        <p>Every placement builds on the last. A placement in Inside Higher Ed feeds search authority. A data study earns AI citations. Coverage compounds instead of resetting.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHO IT'S FOR -->
<section class="band wrap">
  <div class="sec-head">
    <div class="sec-eyebrow">Who it's for</div>
    <h2>Built for teams that need <em class="grad">real coverage</em>.</h2>
    <p>Universities, colleges, edtech companies, and the agencies that serve them.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="forind" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)">
    <a class="ficard" href="/contact">
      <div class="fi" style="background:var(--gold-soft);color:var(--gold-deep)"><i class="ti ti-school"></i></div>
      <h3>Universities & Colleges</h3>
      <p>Full-cycle earned media campaigns for enrollment. Every placement tied to the publications your applicants read and the data that makes your programs credible.</p>
      <span class="more">Book a discovery call <i class="ti ti-calendar"></i></span>
    </a>
    <a class="ficard" href="/contact">
      <div class="fi" style="background:var(--indigo-soft);color:var(--indigo-deep)"><i class="ti ti-device-laptop"></i></div>
      <h3>Edtech & OPMs</h3>
      <p>Category authority through trade press and thought leadership. Be the platform institutions trust because the coverage says so.</p>
      <span class="more">Book a discovery call <i class="ti ti-calendar"></i></span>
    </a>
    <a class="ficard" href="/contact">
      <div class="fi" style="background:var(--coral-soft);color:var(--coral-deep)"><i class="ti ti-briefcase"></i></div>
      <h3>Agencies</h3>
      <p>White-label earned media for your higher-ed clients. You keep the relationship; we deliver the placements.</p>
      <span class="more">Book a discovery call <i class="ti ti-calendar"></i></span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CLOSING -->
<section class="closing">
  <div class="catmos"><div class="cg"></div></div>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="pill-badge"><span class="tagm">Digital PR for Higher Ed</span></div>
    <h2>Let's get your institution <em class="grad">covered</em>.</h2>
    <p>Start with a $500 Earned Media Session — or book a discovery call to scope your campaign.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg"><i class="ti ti-calendar"></i>Book a discovery call</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>